  <sentence alpsent="WR-P-P-H-0000000048.p.19.s.1.xml">Ook <markable head="vatinel" id="markable_351" level="reference" mod="no" ref="markable_49" time="none" type="ident">WOW-woordvoerster Vatinel</markable> is optimistisch .</sentence>
